*Patricia Kane and Dolores Y. Wilkinson, &quot;Survival Strategies: Black Women in &#x27;Ollie Miss&#x27; and &#x27;Cotton Comes to Harlem&#x27; &quot;, &quot;Critique: Studies in Modern Fiction&quot; 16, no.1 (1974): 101-9</text><links>
