*(1989) Divorce Case
*(1990) More Hits From Peta Teanet
*(1991) The Gospel Album with The Special Servants
*(1991) The Real Peta Teanet
*(1992) Saka Naye Jive
*(1992) The Heroes Peta Teanet and Paul Ndlovu 
*(1993) Jahman Teanet
*(1993) Uta ku Tsakisa
*(1994) Peta Will Excite You
*(1995) Double Pashash
*(1996) King Of Shangaan Disco

